- Use Next.js 14 App Router only (no pages/ directory)
- TypeScript strict mode always
- Tailwind utility classes only (no inline styles)
- No class-variance-authority
- All components must be in src/components/
- Use lucide-react for all icons
- Brand colors are in tailwind.config.ts — always use utility classes like bg-primary, text-accent, border-border. Never hardcode hex values in components.
